"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?35/61/36819/abstract/3\">",
"      de Haan TR, van den Akker ES, Porcelijn L, et al. Thrombocytopenia in hydropic fetuses with parvovirus B19 infection: incidence, treatment and correlation with fetal B19 viral load. BJOG 2008; 115:76.",
"     </a>",
